### Prerequisites

- Node.js 20+ and pnpm 8+
- {% if saas_database == "neon" %}Neon{% else %}Supabase{% endif %} account
- {% if saas_auth == "clerk" %}Clerk{% else %}OAuth provider{% endif %} credentials
